#. type: Title ###
#: docs/8.x/hashing.md:90
#, no-wrap
msgid "Determining If A Password Needs To Be Rehashed"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/8.x/hashing.md:93
msgid ""
"The `needsRehash` method provided by the `Hash` facade allows you to "
"determine if the work factor used by the hasher has changed since the "
"password was hashed. Some applications choose to perform this check during "
"the application's authentication process:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/8.x/hashing.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    if (Hash::needsRehash($hashed)) {\n"
"        $hashed = Hash::make('plain-text');\n"
"    }\n"
msgstr ""
